text: Custom House for ExCeL is a Docklands Light Railway (DLR) station at Custom House in London, England which serves the Elizabeth Line. It is near the Royal Docks in the London Borough of Newham. It is in Travelcard Zone 3. Its name comes from the old Custom House, which used to be nearby, and Exhibition Centre, London (ExCeL) which is nearby. Category:Docklands Light Railway stations in the London Borough of Newham
